            <td width="100%"><p align="left">Since 1987 Smartscan has been a trusted source for
            reliable, 3rd party approved and cost effective machine guarding products. Smartscan's
            range of machine safety products includes safety light curtains, safety gate interlocks,
            safety relays, programmable safety relays and safety PLCs. In addition we provide help
            right throughout the machine safety process from initial expert safety advice through
            safety standards advice, risk assessment, safety system design, system installation and
            safety system maintenance. Our products and services are used in all facets of automation
            including electronics, automotive, packaging, aerospace, and specialty machines.</p>
            <p align="left"><b>Our corporate vision is to be the easiest safety automation company for
            our customers, potential customers and distributors to do business with. Contact us for
            your next safeguarding need and let us prove it!</b></p>
            <p align="left">In addition we offer CE marking Services for machines, including
            Declaration of Conformity and Technical File in accordance with the Machinery and other
            associated Directives.</p>
